@startuml sie-governance-sequence-v1

' ============================================================
' VISUAL THEME
' ============================================================

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #57606A
skinparam DefaultFontName "SansSerif"
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

skinparam participantBackgroundColor #F6F8FA
skinparam participantBorderColor #57606A

skinparam sequenceGroupBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceGroupBorderColor #57606A

skinparam sequenceBoxBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam sequenceBoxBorderColor #57606A

skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FFF8C5
skinparam noteBorderColor #57606A

title SIE - Governance Loop to Architecture Mapping - v1

' ============================================================
' PARTICIPANTS BY PLANE
' ============================================================

box "Definition Plane" #E8F4E8
  participant "SDM\n(Systemic Definition Manager)" as SDM
  participant "CSDSL Processor" as CSDSL
  participant "CEL Transpiler" as CEL
end box

box "Description Plane" #E8F0FA
  participant "State Ingestion" as Ingestion
  participant "CSDM Runtime" as CSDM
  participant "Policy Evaluator" as Evaluator
end box

box "Remediation Plane" #FFE0E0
  participant "Behavioral Rules Engine" as Rules
  participant "Action Executor" as Actuator
  participant "Escalation Manager" as Escalation
end box

actor "State Plane" as System
actor "Governance Officer" as Officer

' ============================================================
' SEQUENCE: GOVERNANCE LOOP
' ============================================================

note over SDM, Escalation
  **Governance Loop Execution**
  Maps conceptual loop stages to actual components
end note

== Phase 1: Define Desired State (Definition Plane) ==

Officer -> SDM: Define policy
activate SDM

SDM -> CSDSL: Parse constraints
activate CSDSL
CSDSL --> SDM: AST
deactivate CSDSL

SDM -> CEL: Compile to CEL
activate CEL
CEL --> SDM: Compiled expression
deactivate CEL

SDM -> SDM: Store versioned policy

note right of SDM
  **Conceptual: Desired State**
  
  - Policies = reference input
  - Constraints = comparator rules
  - Rules = controller logic
end note

SDM -->> Evaluator: Publish compiled policy
deactivate SDM

== Phase 2: Observe Measured State (Description Plane) ==

System ->> Ingestion: Events / state changes
activate Ingestion

Ingestion -> CSDM: Normalize to state objects
activate CSDM
CSDM -> CSDM: Store current state
CSDM --> Ingestion: Stored
deactivate CSDM

note right of Ingestion
  **Conceptual: Sensor**
  
  - State Ingestion = collectors
  - CSDM = measured state store
end note

Ingestion -->> Evaluator: Notify state change
deactivate Ingestion

== Phase 3: Compute Error Signal (Description Plane) ==

activate Evaluator
Evaluator -> CSDM: Fetch current state
CSDM --> Evaluator: State object

Evaluator -> Evaluator: Evaluate CEL expressions\n(policy vs state)

alt Violation detected
  note right of Evaluator
    **Conceptual: Comparator**
    
    Error signal = violations
    (gap between desired & actual)
  end note
  
  Evaluator -->> Rules: Emit violation event
else No violation
  Evaluator -> Evaluator: Record compliance
end
deactivate Evaluator

== Phase 4: Compute Control Action (Remediation Plane) ==

activate Rules
Rules -> Rules: Match behavioral rules\nto violation

note right of Rules
  **Conceptual: Controller**
  
  - Rule Matcher
  - Action Selector
  - Remediation Planner
end note

alt Auto-remediation allowed
  Rules -> Actuator: Execute action
  activate Actuator
  
  note right of Actuator
    **Conceptual: Actuator**
    
    - Config changes
    - Scaling
    - Deployments
    - Alerts
  end note
  
  Actuator -> System: Apply remediation
  System --> Actuator: Result
  Actuator -> CSDM: Record action result
  deactivate Actuator
  
else Approval required
  Rules -> Escalation: Create incident
  activate Escalation
  Escalation -> Officer: Request approval
  Officer --> Escalation: Approve/reject
  Escalation --> Rules: Decision
  deactivate Escalation
end

deactivate Rules

== Phase 5: Feedback Loop ==

System ->> Ingestion: Updated state

note over Ingestion, Officer
  **Conceptual: Feedback**
  
  Loop repeats continuously.
  
  - Effectiveness tracked over time
  - Policy refinements fed back to SDM
  - Patterns learned for future actions
end note

Officer <- Evaluator: Compliance reports
Officer -> SDM: Refine policies

@enduml
